    {
      "id": "p1-p1",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "In this lesson, you will say hello, introduce yourself, use do you questions, talk about countries and nationalities, and listen to short introductions."
    },
    {
      "id": "p1-note1",
      "type": "teacher-note",
      "title": "Lesson focus",
      "content": "Keep the lesson simple and oral. Model first, repeat together, then let students answer with real information."
    },
